query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info not in ('other literature','death date','screenplay-teleplay','LD number of sides','quotes','LD spaciality','taglines','LD audio quality','other works','LD frequency response','LD group genre','copyright holder','bottom 10 rank','soundtrack','interviews','tech info','LD label','goofs','books','trade mark') AND (n.name like '%l%') AND k.keyword not like '%assassin%' AND k.keyword not like '%terrorist%' AND k.keyword not like '%chase%' AND k.keyword not like '%spy%' AND (t.title like '%mystery%' OR t.title like '%apple%') AND cct2.kind in ('crew','complete+verified') AND kt.kind not in ('video movie','tv movie','episode','tv mini series','video game','tv series') AND mi_idx.info > '4.0'
